00:09:04.043 --> 00:09:05.711  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[man 2] Out of the way.

135
00:09:06.145 --> 00:09:08.247  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Keep killing him
as we carry him to the vehicle.

136
00:09:10.616 --> 00:09:12.618  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunfire continues]

137
00:09:30.570 --> 00:09:33.573  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So, he's unable to-- To move.

138
00:09:33.639 --> 00:09:35.775  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Is it really this easy?

139
00:09:36.108 --> 00:09:37.577  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Of course it is.

140
00:09:37.643 --> 00:09:39.845  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We've got 20 SAT members.

141
00:09:39.912 --> 00:09:42.782  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
They're not just security guards
this time.

142
00:09:47.787 --> 00:09:51.791  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Actually... he underestimated us humans.

143
00:09:53.292 --> 00:09:55.294  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunfire on TV]

144
00:10:01.334 --> 00:10:02.702  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
If he can't die...

145
00:10:03.869 --> 00:10:06.205  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
then we won't give him the chance to live.

146
00:10:08.207 --> 00:10:09.809  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunfire]

147
00:10:12.345 --> 00:10:14.914  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[man 1] Just a little further.
We're almost to the vehicle.

148
00:10:16.682 --> 00:10:19.385  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[chief] Team 4, reload.
Team 1, take over. Fire.

149
00:10:20.119 --> 00:10:21.153  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunshot]

150
00:10:23.723 --> 00:10:25.291  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[man 2] Does anyone have eyes
on the target?

151
00:10:25.358 --> 00:10:26.258  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Where is it?

152
00:10:26.325 --> 00:10:28.227  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[man 3] There are others.
We've got snipers.

153
00:10:33.933 --> 00:10:35.968  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Gen] Two millimeters to the right.

154
00:10:36.035 --> 00:10:37.970  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Takahashi] Okay.

155
00:10:41.374 --> 00:10:43.042  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chief] Defense team! Shields!

156
00:10:48.014 --> 00:10:49.849  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

157
00:10:49.915 --> 00:10:51.784  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Gen! Takahashi!

158
00:10:52.084 --> 00:10:53.786  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Takahashi] Yeah, we know.

159
00:10:56.355 --> 00:10:57.423  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

160
00:10:59.759 --> 00:11:01.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chief] Do not let this guy revive.

161
00:11:01.427 --> 00:11:03.195  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Do something about the sniper.

162
00:11:04.964 --> 00:11:06.232  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You got the handcuffs off.

163
00:11:06.298 --> 00:11:09.135  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Now all we gotta do
is just give him a chance to revive--

164
00:11:09.201 --> 00:11:10.369  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunshot]

165
00:11:10.436 --> 00:11:11.671  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh?

166
00:11:17.143 --> 00:11:18.711  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[spotter 1] This is Sniper Team 1.

167
00:11:18.778 --> 00:11:20.112  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Target confirmed as an Ajin.

168
00:11:20.846 --> 00:11:22.915  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
On the roof of the building
at your ten o'clock.

169
00:11:23.182 --> 00:11:25.951  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[spotter 2] Sniper Team 2. Target sighted.

170
00:11:26.018 --> 00:11:28.821  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[spotter 3] Sniper Team 3. Target sighted.

171
00:11:28.888 --> 00:11:30.890  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[chief over radio]<i> All right,</i>
<i>just keep killing him.</i>

172
00:11:30.956 --> 00:11:32.958  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunfire]

173
00:11:37.696 --> 00:11:39.732  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Enemy sniper neutralized.

174
00:11:39.799 --> 00:11:41.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okay, resume transport.

175
00:11:46.472 --> 00:11:48.707  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hurry. Just a bit farther.

176
00:11:55.047 --> 00:11:56.382  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[sniper]
What about the other one?

177
00:11:56.449 --> 00:11:58.717  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[spotter] Don't shoot. He's surrendering.

178
00:12:01.854 --> 00:12:04.290  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We've got SAT snipers in three locations.

179
00:12:04.790 --> 00:12:06.192  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
On roof to the south

180
00:12:06.258 --> 00:12:08.194  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
as well as to the north.

181
00:12:09.028 --> 00:12:11.263  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
And on the top floor
of the Mizuno Building.

182
00:12:11.997 --> 00:12:13.065  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Roger that.

183
00:12:21.841 --> 00:12:22.975  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[glass breaking]

184
00:12:26.879 --> 00:12:29.014  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Sniper Team 1 here. We're under fire.

185
00:12:29.081 --> 00:12:30.382  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
There must be another sniper.

186
00:12:35.121 --> 00:12:36.088  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

187
00:12:36.155 --> 00:12:38.324  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Wait, that's...

188
00:12:41.060 --> 00:12:44.530  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps] They really exist?

189
00:12:49.401 --> 00:12:50.870  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oh!

190
00:12:53.472 --> 00:12:55.107  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

191
00:12:56.308 --> 00:12:58.344  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chief]<i> Sniper Team 1? What happened?</i>

192
00:13:02.348 --> 00:13:05.885  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[spotter] Team 1's been taken out.
[sniper] It's an IBM. Get ready.

193
00:13:06.452 --> 00:13:08.020  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Damn it.

194
00:13:08.087 --> 00:13:09.488  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Where is it?

195
00:13:12.791 --> 00:13:13.859  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I can see it. It's coming!

196
00:13:13.926 --> 00:13:15.027  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunshot]

197
00:13:17.163 --> 00:13:18.364  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunts]

198
00:13:25.471 --> 00:13:27.339  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[growls]

199
00:13:28.174 --> 00:13:29.408  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasping]

200
00:13:35.814 --> 00:13:38.117  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

201
00:13:39.051 --> 00:13:41.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It stopped. It stopped!

202
00:13:41.387 --> 00:13:42.388  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
But why?

203
00:13:50.329 --> 00:13:54.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh. You're late... and you missed.

204
00:13:56.335 --> 00:13:58.537  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I can't use this guy for a while.

205
00:13:59.004 --> 00:14:00.239  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Still one more.

206
00:14:02.274 --> 00:14:04.843  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hmm. Guess I'll run.

207
00:14:11.283 --> 00:14:13.152  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Open the doors! Quick!

208
00:14:18.257 --> 00:14:19.925  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hurry and wake up, huh?

209
00:14:19.992 --> 00:14:22.328  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
If we don't back him up,
there gonna take him away.

210
00:14:22.394 --> 00:14:23.462  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

211
00:14:31.136 --> 00:14:32.471  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Team 1 and Team 2 down.

212
00:14:32.538 --> 00:14:34.506  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
At this rate, we can't keep killing him.

213
00:14:34.573 --> 00:14:35.574  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We should retreat.

214
00:14:35.641 --> 00:14:36.909  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Not yet.

215
00:14:38.210 --> 00:14:40.346  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'll take out the enemy's rifle.

216
00:14:43.949 --> 00:14:45.451  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hit the guys with the stretcher.

217
00:14:45.517 --> 00:14:48.053  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
That way he'll have another chance
to revive.

218
00:14:48.120 --> 00:14:49.521  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okay.

219
00:14:50.456 --> 00:14:53.058  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'll knock down the guy in the front.

220
00:14:57.529 --> 00:15:00.065  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
The wind has died down. Go for it.

221
00:15:00.132 --> 00:15:01.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Roger.

222
00:15:01.967 --> 00:15:03.302  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunshot]

223
00:15:06.038 --> 00:15:08.040  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chief]<i> You fool! What are you doing?</i>

224
00:15:08.574 --> 00:15:10.476  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-[grunts]
-I got it.

225
00:15:17.516 --> 00:15:20.119  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps] What's that?

226
00:15:21.620 --> 00:15:25.257  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Okuyama] You should use both hands
to keep it steady, Tanaka.

227
00:15:25.324 --> 00:15:27.493  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[sighs] Okay, whatever.

228
00:15:27.559 --> 00:15:28.460  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
BOTH:
Huh?

229
00:15:29.295 --> 00:15:30.162  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

230
00:15:30.696 --> 00:15:32.564  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[panting]

231
00:15:35.501 --> 00:15:37.503  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chuckling]

232
00:15:42.374 --> 00:15:44.376  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

233
00:15:45.077 --> 00:15:46.946  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's no good. It's broken.

234
00:15:47.012 --> 00:15:48.213  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
How's Sato doing?

235
00:15:48.280 --> 00:15:50.182  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm trying to find him.

236
00:15:50.683 --> 00:15:52.418  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[man 1] You're in the way. Move.

237
00:15:53.953 --> 00:15:55.354  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Good morning.
[man 1] Ugh.

238
00:15:56.388 --> 00:15:58.057  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Go to hell!

239
00:15:59.291 --> 00:16:01.293  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Damn it! No good.

240
00:16:03.162 --> 00:16:04.163  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

241
00:16:05.464 --> 00:16:07.066  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
The bullets!

242
00:16:08.367 --> 00:16:10.202  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Huh? What the--?

243
00:16:10.970 --> 00:16:13.038  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[man 1] What is that?
[man 2] What?

244
00:16:13.405 --> 00:16:14.974  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Good try.

245
00:16:15.040 --> 00:16:16.475  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You were almost there.

246
00:16:20.145 --> 00:16:21.613  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Gen] Awesome!

247
00:16:21.680 --> 00:16:24.717  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[laughing] Yeah! Go, Sato!

248
00:16:25.417 --> 00:16:27.619  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Look at this guy. He's not human.

249
00:16:28.520 --> 00:16:30.556  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
He's a monster, for sure.

250
00:16:30.622 --> 00:16:32.358  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Now, settle down.

251
00:16:36.395 --> 00:16:38.030  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Don't shoot!

252
00:16:39.565 --> 00:16:40.699  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Sato] Too late.

253
00:16:48.173 --> 00:16:49.475  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunts]

254
00:16:55.347 --> 00:16:56.348  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[man] Don't shoot!

255
00:17:07.459 --> 00:17:08.694  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gunfire]

256
00:17:20.639 --> 00:17:22.107  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

257
00:17:38.724 --> 00:17:40.259  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Whew.

258
00:17:40.325 --> 00:17:41.693  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'm beat.

259
00:17:54.506 --> 00:17:57.342  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[cameraman] There! It's Sato!
[reporter] Follow him!

260
00:18:10.389 --> 00:18:13.525  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's times like this I hate the press.

261
00:18:18.430 --> 00:18:19.598  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[helicopter crashes]

262
00:18:21.366 --> 00:18:23.402  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[explosion]

263
00:18:26.205 --> 00:18:27.506  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[grunting]

264
00:18:27.573 --> 00:18:29.741  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[reporter on TV]<i> A-- A news helicopter</i>
<i>has crashed.</i>

265
00:18:29.808 --> 00:18:31.643  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>It may have been hit by stray gunfire.</i>

266
00:18:31.710 --> 00:18:33.645  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>It's burning</i>
<i>right in the middle of the street.</i>

267
00:18:34.313 --> 00:18:35.881  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

268
00:18:36.615 --> 00:18:38.584  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Kouma] What's the status of the SAT unit?

269
00:18:38.650 --> 00:18:40.419  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Where has Sato gone?

270
00:18:40.486 --> 00:18:41.620  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's no good.

271
00:18:41.687 --> 00:18:44.423  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The local security cameras
have been hacked.

272
00:18:44.490 --> 00:18:46.558  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
The SAT unit must have been wiped out.

273
00:18:49.194 --> 00:18:51.196  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasping]

274
00:18:56.602 --> 00:18:57.769  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
No good, huh?

275
00:19:01.740 --> 00:19:03.909  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'd say we got played.

276
00:19:04.376 --> 00:19:05.644  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[snickers]

277
00:19:05.878 --> 00:19:07.679  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Game, set and match.

278
00:19:15.854 --> 00:19:17.656  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Yamanaka] Kei!

279
00:19:17.723 --> 00:19:20.559  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Could you give me a hand here?

280
00:19:28.700 --> 00:19:31.436  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[reporter on TV] <i>The search</i>
